- The Captain should have shot at them. - Huh?

997
01:20:32,990 --> 01:20:36,490
海鸥是食腐动物 多数的鸟类都是
Gulls are scavengers, anyway. Most birds are.

998
01:20:36,580 --> 01:20:39,120
拿起枪 让它们在地球上消失吧！
Get yourselves guns and wipe them off the face of the Earth!

999
01:20:40,250 --> 01:20:43,210
- 那是不可能的 - 为什么？
That would hardly be possible. Why not, Mrs. Bundy?

1000
01:20:43,960 --> 01:20:46,670
因为当今世界上
Because there are 8,650 species

1001
01:20:46,750 --> 01:20:49,470
有8650种鸟类，卡特先生
of birds in the world today, Mr. Carter.

1002
01:20:49,550 --> 01:20:53,340
光是美国估计就有
It is estimated that 5,750,000,000 birds

1003
01:20:53,430 --> 01:20:55,350
五十七亿五千万只鸟
live in the United States alone.

1004
01:20:55,430 --> 01:20:57,350
世界五大洲…
The five continents of the world...

1005
01:20:57,430 --> 01:21:00,310
杀光它们！ 除掉这些麻烦的动物
Kill them all. Get rid of the messy animals.

1006
01:21:00,390 --> 01:21:03,520
…可能就有超过一千亿只鸟
...probably contain more than 100 billion birds.

1007
01:21:03,600 --> 01:21:07,320
- 世界末日到了 - 那些海鸥一定是想吃鱼
It's the end of the world. Those gulls must have been after the fish.

1008
01:21:07,400 --> 01:21:10,240
- 当然！ - 孩子们，快把饭吃完
Of course! Hurry up, children. Finish your lunch.

1009
01:21:10,320 --> 01:21:13,030
妈妈，鸟会吃掉我们吗？
Are the birds gonna eat us, Mommy?

1010
01:21:13,110 --> 01:21:15,870
我们也许太过小题大做了
Hell, maybe we're all getting a little carried away by this.

1011
01:21:15,950 --> 01:21:19,290
几只鸟确实很反常 但没理由相信…
Admittedly, a few birds did act strange, but that's no reason to believe that...

1012
01:21:19,370 --> 01:21:23,540
我说过了，这不止是几只鸟 有海鸥、乌鸦、雨燕…
I keep telling you, this isn't a few birds. These are gulls, crows, swifts...

1013
01:21:23,620 --> 01:21:26,840
我没听说过 不同种类的鸟会聚集在一起
I have never known birds of different species to flock together.

1014
01:21:26,920 --> 01:21:29,420
那是无法想像的
The very concept is unimaginable.

1015
01:21:29,510 --> 01:21:32,720
如果真的发生了 我们根本没机会！
Why, if that happened, we wouldn't have a chance!

1016
01:21:32,800 --> 01:21:35,050
我们怎么可能斗得过它们？
How could we possibly hope to fight them?

1017
01:21:35,140 --> 01:21:38,220
我们不可能赢 说得对，邦迪太太
We couldn't, you're right. You're right, Mrs. Bundy.

1018
01:21:38,310 --> 01:21:39,470
发生什么事了？
What's the matter? Something wrong out here?

1019
01:21:39,560 --> 01:21:41,350
我们正在打仗，山姆
We're fighting a war, Sam.

1020
01:21:42,180 --> 01:21:43,640
打仗？ 跟谁打？
A war? Against who?

1021
01:21:43,730 --> 01:21:47,230
- 跟鸟打！ - 真庆幸你们以为这很有趣
Against birds! I'm glad you all think this is so amusing.

1022
01:21:47,310 --> 01:21:48,980
你们快把孩子们吓死了
You've frightened the children half out of their wits.

1023
01:21:49,070 --> 01:21:50,190
若这位小姐说
If the young lady said

1024
01:21:50,280 --> 01:21:53,110
她看见学生被攻击 你们为何不相信她？
she saw the attack at a school, why don't you believe her?

1025
01:21:53,200 --> 01:21:56,120
- 攻击？ 谁攻击学生了？ - 鸟、乌鸦
What attack? Who attacked the school? Birds did. Crows.

1026
01:21:56,660 --> 01:21:58,530
你们只顾着争辩！
You're all sitting around here debating!

1027
01:21:58,620 --> 01:22:00,910
你们想它们接下来会怎样？ 撞破窗户？
What do you want them to do next? Crash through that window?

1028
01:22:00,990 --> 01:22:03,960
- 妈妈！ - 外套穿上
Mommy! Shh. Put on your coat.

1029
01:22:07,080 --> 01:22:10,380
你们何不回家把门窗锁好？
Why don't you all go home, lock your doors and windows?

1030
01:22:10,460 --> 01:22:13,260
- 到旧金山最快的路线是？ - 高速公路，女士
What's the fastest way to San Francisco? The freeway, ma'am.

1031
01:22:13,340 --> 01:22:14,510
怎么走？
How do I find it?

1032
01:22:14,590 --> 01:22:17,010
我也要去高速公路 可以跟着我
I'm going out that way, lady. You can follow me.

1033
01:22:17,090 --> 01:22:21,010
- 那我们马上走吧 - 我的酒还没喝完
Well, then let's leave now. Haven't finished my drink yet.

1034
01:22:22,850 --> 01:22:24,770
我尽快赶来了，凯西在哪里？
I got here as fast as I could. Where's Cathy?

1035
01:22:24,850 --> 01:22:27,600
- 她跟安妮在一起，她没事 - 艾尔，学生被攻击时
She's with Annie. She's all right. Al, why aren't you over at the school,

1036
01:22:27,600 --> 01:22:28,860
你怎么没赶到学校？
where the attack was?

1037
01:22:28,940 --> 01:22:31,110
因为我刚刚人在丹佛西特家
'Cause I just got back from Dan Fawcett's place, that's why.

1038
01:22:31,190 --> 01:22:34,150
- 他昨晚被鸟杀死了 - 什么？
He was killed last night by birds. What?

1039
01:22:34,240 --> 01:22:36,200
慢着，米契，你还不能确定
Now, hold it, Mitch. You don't know that for a fact.

1040
01:22:36,280 --> 01:22:38,370
马龙先生，事实是什么？
What are the facts, Mr. Malone?

1041
01:22:38,450 --> 01:22:40,830
圣塔罗沙警方认为是重罪谋杀
The Santa Rosa Police think it's a felony murder.

1042
01:22:40,910 --> 01:22:42,830
他们认为是小偷闯进去杀了他
They think a burglar broke in, killed him.

1043
01:22:42,910 --> 01:22:45,040
那满地的死鸟又该如何解释？
How do you explain the dead birds all over the floor?

1044
01:22:45,120 --> 01:22:48,380
圣塔罗沙警方认为 鸟是在他被杀害后才飞进来的
Santa Rosa Police figure they got in after the old man was killed.

1045
01:22:48,460 --> 01:22:51,000
圣塔罗沙警方 今天有到学校去吗？
Were the Santa Rosa Police at your school today?

1046
01:22:52,960 --> 01:22:55,300
- 你要来吗？ - 冷静点，女士
Are you coming? Now take it easy, lady.

1047
01:22:55,380 --> 01:22:57,970
这里看不见一只鸟！
There isn't a bird anywhere in sight!

1048
01:22:58,050 --> 01:23:01,810
看看天上的鸟 它们不播种也不收获
"Look at the birds of the air. They do not sow or reap.

1049
01:23:01,890 --> 01:23:05,560
“但你们的天父喂养它们”
"Yet your heavenly Father feeds them."

1050
01:23:05,640 --> 01:23:08,440
圣塔克鲁兹 去年也发生了这种事
Say, something like this happened in Santa Cruz last year.

1051
01:23:08,520 --> 01:23:11,230
海鸥遮盖了整座城镇
The town was just covered with seagulls.

1052
01:23:11,320 --> 01:23:14,860
- 请快把你的酒喝完 - 没错，我想起来了
Will you please finish your drink? That's right, sir. I recall it.

1053
01:23:14,940 --> 01:23:17,450
一大群海鸥在雾中迷路
A large flock of seagulls got lost in a fog,

1054
01:23:17,530 --> 01:23:20,160
朝着光线飞进了镇上
and headed into the town where all the lights were.

1055
01:23:20,240 --> 01:23:23,450
那也造成了不少麻烦 冲进建筑物里之类的
They made some mess, too, smashing into buildings and everything.

1056
01:23:23,540 --> 01:23:24,790
鸟就会制造麻烦
They always make a mess.

1057
01:23:24,870 --> 01:23:28,000
重点是没人为此感到不满
The point is that no one seemed to be upset about it.

1058
01:23:28,080 --> 01:23:31,500
它们隔天早上就离开了 好像什么事都没发生一样
They were all gone next morning, just as though nothing at all had happened.

1059
01:23:31,590 --> 01:23:34,840
- 可怜的东西 - 我要走了！你来不来？
Poor things. I'm leaving! Are you coming?

1060
01:23:34,920 --> 01:23:36,840
来了！
All right, all right!

1061
01:23:39,220 --> 01:23:41,510
希望你们能搞清楚这件事！
Well, hope you folks figure this thing out!

1062
01:23:41,600 --> 01:23:43,310
世界末日到了！
It's the end of the world!

1063
01:23:44,560 --> 01:23:47,270
我该回罐头工厂了 迪克，多少钱？
I better get back to the cannery. What do I owe you, Deke?

1064
01:23:47,350 --> 01:23:49,060
赛巴斯汀，等一下
Sebastian, hold it a minute.

1065
01:23:49,140 --> 01:23:52,020
- 我不想大惊小怪… - 没人说你是，米契
I don't want to be an alarmist about this... No one ever said you were, Mitch.

1066
01:23:52,110 --> 01:23:54,480
我想我们麻烦大了 我不知道这件事的起因
I think we're in real trouble. I don't know how this started, or why,

1067
01:23:54,570 --> 01:23:56,780
但我知道这是真的 我们不能不管
but I know it's here and we'd be crazy to ignore it.

1068
01:23:56,860 --> 01:23:59,820
- 不管什么？  “鸟的战争”？ - 对，“鸟的战争”
To ignore what? The "bird war"? Yes, the "bird war."

1069
01:23:59,910 --> 01:24:01,820
鸟类攻击、瘟疫… 随怎么称呼
The bird attack, plague... Call it what you like,

1070
01:24:01,910 --> 01:24:04,700
它们正在某处聚集 它们会回来的，我敢保证
they're massing out there someplace, and they'll be back. You can count on it.

1071
01:24:04,790 --> 01:24:07,040
- 荒谬 - 过来一下
Ridiculous. Come here.

1072
01:24:07,120 --> 01:24:08,540
除非我们采取行动
Unless we do something right now,

1073
01:24:08,620 --> 01:24:10,210
除非我们疏散博德加湾…
unless we get Bodega Bay on the move, they...

1074
01:24:10,290 --> 01:24:12,250
听着，米契
Look, Mitch.

1075
01:24:13,340 --> 01:24:16,590
就算这是真的，就算这些鸟…
Even if this is true, even if all the birds...

1076
01:24:16,670 --> 01:24:20,470
- 你不相信这是真的？ - 米契，我不相信
Don't you believe it's true? No, Mitch, frankly I don't.

1077
01:24:20,550 --> 01:24:23,680
- 这没道理… - 这确实发生了，还没道理吗？
There's no reason. I... Well, it's happening. Isn't that a reason?

1078
01:24:23,760 --> 01:24:26,220
- 我爱博德加湾… - 那就协助我
I like Bodega Bay as well as the next man... Fine, then help me.

1079
01:24:26,310 --> 01:24:28,640
你是镇上的要人 若你帮我，镇民都会听话
You're an important man in this town. If you help, they all will.

1080
01:24:28,730 --> 01:24:30,940
怎么帮？ 你想怎么做？
Help how? What do you want to do?

1081
01:24:31,020 --> 01:24:32,940
邦迪太太提到圣塔克鲁兹的事
Mrs. Bundy said something about Santa Cruz.

1082
01:24:33,020 --> 01:24:35,570
海鸥在雾中迷路 朝着光线飞去
About seagulls getting lost in a fog and flying in towards the lights.

1083
01:24:35,650 --> 01:24:37,900
- 这时节不会起雾！ - 那就用人工造雾！
We don't have fog this time of year! Make our own fog!

1084
01:24:37,990 --> 01:24:38,940
要怎么做？
How do you figure to do that?

1085
01:24:39,030 --> 01:24:40,280
学军队使用烟雾罐
We can use smoke pots, the way the Army uses them.

1086
01:24:40,360 --> 01:24:41,490
你们看！
Look!

1087
01:24:46,160 --> 01:24:49,410
它们又攻击了 梅兰妮，待在这里，走吧，艾尔！
They're attacking again. Melanie, you stay in here. Come on, Al!

1088
01:24:55,710 --> 01:24:56,750
小心！
Look out!

1089
01:25:26,740 --> 01:25:29,240
汽油流了满地 那个男人在点烟！
Look at the gas. That man's lighting a cigar!

1090
01:25:31,580 --> 01:25:33,870
嘿！听着！别把火柴丢地上！
Hey, you! Watch out! Don't drop that match!

1091
01:25:33,960 --> 01:25:35,250
快离开！
Get out of there!

1092
01:25:35,330 --> 01:25:37,090
- 先生，快跑！ - 小心！
- Mister, run! - Watch out!

1093
01:25:37,630 --> 01:25:39,500
注意！小心啊！
Look out! Look out! Watch out!

1094
01:26:29,180 --> 01:26:30,180
嘿！
Hey!

1095
01:28:40,390 --> 01:28:42,190
它们为什么要这么做？
Why are they doing this?

1096
01:28:43,400 --> 01:28:45,440
它们为什么要这么做？
Why are they doing this?

1097
01:28:46,690 --> 01:28:49,400
别人说在来了之后 整件事就开始了！
They said when you got here, the whole thing started!

1098
01:28:52,700 --> 01:28:56,200
是谁？ 是什么东西？
Who are you? What are you?

1099
01:28:56,330 --> 01:28:58,540
从哪里来的？
Where did you come from?

1100
01:28:59,700 --> 01:29:01,920
我认为这都是造成的
I think you're the cause of all this.

1101
01:29:03,080 --> 01:29:05,460
我想是恶魔！恶魔！
I think you're evil! Evil!

1102
01:29:08,090 --> 01:29:10,090
天啊！
Oh, God!

1103
01:29:14,890 --> 01:29:16,600
它们离开了！
I think they're going!

1104
01:29:17,310 --> 01:29:19,220
我们可以去安妮家接凯西了
We can get Cathy at Annie's now.

1105
01:29:54,090 --> 01:29:55,390
乌鸦又来了
- The crows again. - Shh!

1106
01:30:00,270 --> 01:30:01,560
走吧
Come on.

1107
01:30:32,550 --> 01:30:35,510
不，待在这里
Oh, no. Stay here. Stay here.

1108
01:30:44,060 --> 01:30:47,100
凯西！凯西在哪里？
Cathy! Where's Cathy?

1109
01:31:19,470 --> 01:31:21,180
米契，住手！
Mitch, don't!

1110
01:31:48,960 --> 01:31:51,880
别把她留在那里，米契
Oh, don't leave her there, Mitch.

1111
01:32:54,520 --> 01:32:55,690
走吧
Come on.

1112
01:33:27,390 --> 01:33:31,020
我们送蜜雪儿回家后
When we got back from taking Michele home,

1113
01:33:33,520 --> 01:33:36,150
我们听见了爆炸声
we heard the explosion

1114
01:33:36,230 --> 01:33:38,650
我们就到外头查看
and we went outside to see what it was.

1115
01:33:38,900 --> 01:33:43,030
鸟一下子聚集过来！
All at once the birds were everywhere!

1116
01:33:44,160 --> 01:33:47,030
她急忙把我推进屋里
All at once she pushed me inside,

1117
01:33:47,120 --> 01:33:49,040
鸟盖在她身上！
and they covered her!

1118
01:33:49,120 --> 01:33:52,710
安妮…她把我推进屋里！
Annie... She pushed me inside!

1119
01:34:08,100 --> 01:34:10,310
再给我一片木板
Give me another one, darling.

1120
01:34:17,150 --> 01:34:19,070
它们在那边聚集多久了？
How long have they been gathering there?

1121
01:34:19,150 --> 01:34:21,070
大概15分钟
Oh, about 15 minutes.

1122
01:34:25,910 --> 01:34:27,870
这似乎有个模式
Seems like a pattern, doesn't it?

1123
01:34:29,620 --> 01:34:33,120
它们攻击之后就消失 接着再开始聚集
They strike, then disappear, and then start massing again.

1124
01:34:41,500 --> 01:34:43,970
看起来没什么不同，对吧？
Doesn't look so very different, does it?

1125
01:34:44,050 --> 01:34:46,300
像一阵烟笼罩着镇上…
A little smoke hanging over the town, otherwise...

1126
01:34:48,550 --> 01:34:49,850
要再联络父亲吗？
You want to try your father again?

1127
01:34:49,930 --> 01:34:52,220
不，我刚刚试过了 电话不通
No, I tried a little while ago. The phone's dead.

1128
01:34:52,310 --> 01:34:54,180
- 但我们还有电力吧？ - 有
- Still got power, haven't we? - Yes.

1129
01:34:54,930 --> 01:34:57,850
米契，电台传出消息了
Mitch, I'm getting something on the radio.

1130
01:34:57,940 --> 01:34:59,270
走吧
Come on.

1131
01:35:06,070 --> 01:35:08,320
我收不到当地电台
I can't get any of the local stations.

1132
01:35:08,410 --> 01:35:10,370
这应该是旧金山的电台
I think this is San Francisco.

1133
01:35:10,450 --> 01:35:13,950
“…和一组专业团队” 结束
"...and the work of a team of professionals." End quote.

1134
01:35:14,040 --> 01:35:16,500
今早在博德加湾 有一大群乌鸦
In Bodega Bay early this morning, a large flock of crows

1135
01:35:16,580 --> 01:35:20,040
攻击因防火演习 而正在离校的学生
attacked a group of children who were leaving the school during a fire drill.

1136
01:35:20,130 --> 01:35:23,630
一位女孩因此受到重伤 被送往圣塔罗沙的医院
One little girl was seriously injured and taken to the hospital in Santa Rosa,

1137
01:35:23,710 --> 01:35:25,970
但多数学生都很平安
but the majority of children reached safety.

1138
01:35:26,050 --> 01:35:28,430
我们收到镇上 还有另一起攻击事件
We understand there was another attack on the town,

1139
01:35:28,510 --> 01:35:30,680
但资讯还不完全
but this information is rather sketchy.

1140
01:35:30,760 --> 01:35:32,680
到目前为止 还没有消息指出
So far, no word has come through

1141
01:35:32,760 --> 01:35:35,270
是否还有更多攻击事件
to show if there have been further attacks.

1142
01:35:35,350 --> 01:35:37,810
今日的国内新闻，华盛顿…
On the national scene today, in Washington...

1143
01:35:37,890 --> 01:35:39,900
就这样？
Well, is that all?

1144
01:35:41,480 --> 01:35:44,610
我得再拿些木头进来 绝不能让火熄灭
I'll have to get some more wood in. Mustn't let this fire go out.

1145
01:35:46,280 --> 01:35:48,910
- 米契，你有封死阁楼的窗户吗？ - 都封好了
Did you get the windows in the attic, Mitch? Yes, I got them all, dear.

1146
01:35:48,990 --> 01:35:51,240
- 你觉得它们何时会攻击？ - 我不知道
When do you think they'll come? I don't know.

1147
01:35:51,320 --> 01:35:53,370
若有更大型的鸟 它们会冲进屋子里的
If there are bigger birds, Mitch, they'll get into the house.

1148
01:35:53,450 --> 01:35:55,950
- 我们只得冒这个险 - 也许我们该离开
Well, it's just a chance we'll have to take. Maybe we ought to leave.

1149
01:35:56,040 --> 01:35:57,960
现在不行！ 它们正在外头聚集
No, not now! Not while they're massing out there.

1150
01:35:58,040 --> 01:36:00,380
- 那要何时？ - 我们再看看
When? We'll just see what happens.

1151
01:36:00,460 --> 01:36:02,000
- 我们要去哪？ - 我不知道
- Where will we go? - I don't know.

1152
01:36:02,090 --> 01:36:03,290
目前我们很安全
I think we're safe here for the time being.

1153
01:36:03,380 --> 01:36:05,760
- 我们去捡木头 - 木头烧光了怎么办？
Let's get the wood in now. What happens when you run out of wood?

1154
01:36:05,840 --> 01:36:08,510
- 我不知道！我们可以拆家具 - 你不知道！
I don't know! We'll break up the furniture. You don't know!

1155
01:36:08,590 --> 01:36:10,470
你何时才会知道？ 到时我们都死了！
You don't know! When will you know? When we're all dead!

1156
01:36:11,550 --> 01:36:13,890
如果你爸在的话…
If only your father were here...

1157
01:36:17,350 --> 01:36:21,350
对不起，米契
I'm sorry. I'm sorry, Mitch.

1158
01:36:23,610 --> 01:36:26,190
去煮点咖啡喝，好吗？
Make yourself some coffee, won't you?

1159
01:36:29,360 --> 01:36:31,490
在假定总统的任务时
"In assuming the tasks of the presidency,

1160
01:36:31,570 --> 01:36:34,330
“我认为少有世代…”
"I said that few generations..."

1161
01:36:40,210 --> 01:36:43,420
- 它们要去哪里？ - 内陆某处
Where are they heading? Somewhere inland.

1162
01:36:44,250 --> 01:36:46,500
- 圣塔罗沙？ - 也许吧
Santa Rosa? Maybe.

1163
01:36:46,590 --> 01:36:48,720
走吧，我们去捡木头
Come on. Let's get the wood.

1164
01:37:26,590 --> 01:37:30,670
- 米契，我能把爱情鸟拿进来吗？ - 不行！
Mitch? Can I bring the lovebirds in here? No!

1165
01:37:30,760 --> 01:37:34,340
- 妈妈，它们在笼子里 - 它们也是鸟，不是吗？
But, Mom, they're in a cage. They're birds, aren't they?

1166
01:37:37,390 --> 01:37:39,970
让它们待在厨房吧，亲爱的
Let's leave them in the kitchen, huh, honey?

1167
01:38:27,900 --> 01:38:32,110
米契，鸟为什么要这么做？
Mitch, why are they doing this, the birds?

1168
01:38:32,190 --> 01:38:36,360
- 我们不知道，亲爱的 - 它们为什么要杀人？
We don't know, honey. Why are they trying to kill people?

1169
01:38:36,450 --> 01:38:38,490
我希望我知道原因
I wish I could say.

1170
01:39:55,740 --> 01:39:57,490
我不太舒服，梅兰妮
I'm sick, Melanie.

1171
01:39:59,570 --> 01:40:02,870
- 我想… - 我陪去
I want to... I'll go with you.

1172
01:44:38,270 --> 01:44:39,770
它们走了
They're going.

1173
01:45:51,590 --> 01:45:52,760
米契？
Mitch?

1174
01:48:54,270 --> 01:48:55,440
米契！
Oh, Mitch!

1175
01:49:08,700 --> 01:49:11,040
带凯西和莉迪雅离开这里
Get Cathy and Lydia out of here.

1176
01:49:13,210 --> 01:49:15,920
梅兰妮！
Melanie! Melanie!

1177
01:49:29,580 --> 01:49:30,580
Melanie!

1178
01:50:02,170 --> 01:50:05,430
可怜的东西！
Oh, poor thing! Poor thing!

1179
01:50:05,510 --> 01:50:07,720
去拿点水 绷带和消毒药水过来，快！
Listen, get some water, bandages, and antiseptic. Quickly!

1180
01:50:07,810 --> 01:50:10,100
绷带，太可怕了
Bandages. It's terrible.

1181
01:50:14,100 --> 01:50:16,060
凯西，拿白兰地过来
Cathy, get some brandy.

1182
01:50:27,530 --> 01:50:30,160
别怕！没事了
No, no, no! No, no, it's all right.

1183
01:50:30,240 --> 01:50:32,160
好了，没事了
No, it's all right, it's all right, it's all right.

1184
01:50:32,250 --> 01:50:35,330
没事了
It's all right. It's all right. No.

1185
01:51:03,280 --> 01:51:05,240
凯西，拿油灯过来
Cathy, get the lamp.

1186
01:51:20,670 --> 01:51:22,300
我们得送她去医院
We've got to get her to a hospital.

1187
01:51:22,380 --> 01:51:25,130
- 不行，我们没地方可去 - 旧金山
We can't, Mitch. There's no place we can go. There's San Francisco.

1188
01:51:25,260 --> 01:51:27,590
- 我们撑不到那里 - 我们得试试
We'd never make it. We have to try.

1189
01:51:27,680 --> 01:51:30,760
我们走海湾山路 就不必穿过镇上了
We'll go by way of Bay Hill Road. Then we don't have to go through town.

1190
01:51:30,850 --> 01:51:32,760
我们不能待在这里 她需要帮助！
We can't stay here. She needs help!

1191
01:51:33,430 --> 01:51:35,680
我好怕，非常害怕
I'm frightened. Terribly frightened.

1192
01:51:37,640 --> 01:51:39,400
我不知道外面有什么东西
I don't know what's outside there.

1193
01:51:40,770 --> 01:51:43,860
我们最好在 下次攻击到来之前出发
We better get started before another attack comes.

1194
01:51:43,940 --> 01:51:46,700
我们开梅兰妮的车 那会比开卡车快
We'll take Melanie's car. That'll be faster than the truck.

1195
01:51:46,780 --> 01:51:49,360
- 能替她包扎好吗？ - 我尽量
Can you finish the bandaging? I'll try.

1196
01:51:49,450 --> 01:51:50,780
好
All right.

1197
01:51:57,540 --> 01:52:02,130
米契？ 用车上的收音机 听听有什么消息
Mitch? See if you can get anything on the car radio.

1198
01:54:01,330 --> 01:54:03,870
鸟类攻击事件目前已缓和
The bird attacks have subsided for the time being.

1199
01:54:03,960 --> 01:54:07,040
博德加湾似乎是攻击的中心 虽然赛巴斯托波和圣塔罗沙
Bodega Bay seems to be the center, though there are reports of minor attacks

1200
01:54:07,130 --> 01:54:10,170
也传出了轻微的攻击事件
on Sebastopol and a few on Santa Rosa.

1201
01:54:10,260 --> 01:54:12,760
博德加湾周围已设满路障
Bodega Bay has been cordoned off by roadblocks.

1202
01:54:12,840 --> 01:54:14,800
多数的镇民已设法逃出
Most of the townspeople have managed to get out,

1203
01:54:14,890 --> 01:54:17,720
但仍有少数居民受困
but there are still some isolated pockets of people.

1204
01:54:17,800 --> 01:54:21,180
至于下一步该怎么做 当局还没有决定
No decision has been arrived at yet as to what the next step will be,

1205
01:54:21,270 --> 01:54:24,440
但已有人开始讨论 是否该派军队进驻
but there's been some discussion as to whether the military should go in.

1206
01:54:24,520 --> 01:54:26,190
鸟类攻击似乎是阵歇性的
It appears that the bird attacks come in waves,

1207
01:54:26,270 --> 01:54:28,190
中间的间隔时间很长
with long intervals between.

1208
01:54:28,270 --> 01:54:31,320
攻击原因目前还不明朗
The reason for this does not seem clear as yet.

1209
01:56:22,260 --> 01:56:24,310
你有从电台上听到什么吗？
Did you hear anything on the radio?

1210
01:56:24,390 --> 01:56:26,890
没关系，来吧
It's all right. Come on.

1211
01:57:05,260 --> 01:57:07,600
不，不要！
No. No!

1212
01:57:37,090 --> 01:57:38,300
米契？
Mitch?

1213
01:57:40,470 --> 01:57:41,800
待在那里
Stay there.

1214
01:57:49,720 --> 01:57:52,060
米契，我能带爱情鸟走吗？
Can I bring the lovebirds, Mitch?

1215
01:57:52,140 --> 01:57:54,400
它们没有伤害人
They haven't harmed anyone.
